INSERT INTO memory_note_chunks (
	chunk_id,
	note_id,
	chunk_index,
	start_offset,
	end_offset,
	text,
	embedding_version
)
VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7)
ON CONFLICT (chunk_id) DO UPDATE
SET
	text = EXCLUDED.text,
	start_offset = EXCLUDED.start_offset,
	end_offset = EXCLUDED.end_offset
